Retaining Wall Sleepers & Steel Calculator

Calculate how many concrete sleepers and steel posts you need. Just choose the sleeper length you will use, enter the estimated wall length and height and the requirements for concrete and steel will appear on the right. You can purchase concrete sleepers or steel posts from our online shop or give us a call at 0485 856 986, alternatively, get a quote on your calculations below by clicking the “Get a Quote on Above” button.
